The paper proposes two models that combine convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and recurrent neural networks (RNNs) for accurate forecasting on correlated time series. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
